1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 19=

4
00:00:21,679 --> 00:00:22,719
The Qi-Condensed Sword!

5
00:00:23,359 --> 00:00:25,280
I never thought Song Qingbo

6
00:00:25,399 --> 00:00:27,199
had mastered the Zhougong Sword Art.

7
00:00:27,399 --> 00:00:29,519
He's even mastered its final stage,

8
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,120
the Qi-Condensed Sword.

9
00:00:31,399 --> 00:00:32,560
I've heard this technique

10
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:34,119
draws on a lifetime's worth
of vital energy

11
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:37,200
and condenses it into
a massive sword of qi.

12
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:39,560
It has earth-shattering power,

13
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:43,240
but it also burns through
a huge amount of genuine qi.

14
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:46,799
Song Qingbo is staking his life
on one final attack.

15
00:00:46,799 --> 00:00:49,240
Peng Dasheng, accept your fate.

16
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:51,840
Today, you die.

17
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:01,640
Stay back.

18
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:06,120
This is between him and me.

19
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:09,040
I'll finish him myself.

20
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,640
So what if I was born
with sealed meridians?

21
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,439
So what if I'm destined to die?

22
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:20,799
I decide

23
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,239
my own fate.

24
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:42,760
Peng Dasheng, accept your fate.

25
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:45,319
Today, you die.

26
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,840
All-Cleaving Slash!

27
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:13,759
How can your blade intent
be so powerful?

28
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:15,199
Because my killing intent

29
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,719
is ten thousand times stronger.

30
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:34,240
Xiaojiu,

31
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,960
I'll hunt down everyone
who ever hurt you,

32
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:42,560
one by one,

33
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,599
and avenge you.

34
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,840
Amitabha.

35
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,439
Good and evil always get
what they deserve.

36
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:57,759
Heaven's justice never fails.

37
00:02:57,919 --> 00:03:00,319
Mr. Peng has rid the martial world
of a great menace.

38
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,919
He deserves great credit.

39
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,919
We don't need to look further.

40
00:03:05,159 --> 00:03:06,919
Let Mr. Peng command the allied forces.

41
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,879
What do you all say?

42
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,319
Wait.

43
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,840
I have a question for Mr. Peng.

44
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:29,240
Are your parents still living?

45
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,960
Mr. Qiu, why does that matter?

46
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,599
In the martial world,

47
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:35,039
a man's lineage determines his standing.

48
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:37,919
Please answer honestly, Mr. Peng.

49
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,599
I was still a baby

50
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,400
when my father sent me back to my sect.

51
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,680
I haven't seen either

52
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,560
of my parents since.

53
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,000
Then you can't prove

54
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,400
who your father was.

55
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:52,120
Mr. Peng, I mean no offense.

56
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:54,120
But if you can't even explain

57
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,039
where you came from,

58
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,199
how can everyone trust you

59
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:59,199
with their lives?

60
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,039
No, no.

61
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:03,039
I only came here for revenge.

62
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,639
I don't want to command
the allied forces.

63
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,680
Now that my enemy is dead,

64
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,199
I should be going.

65
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,039
Farewell.

66
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,400
I can prove who he is.

67
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:21,079
Twenty years ago, the Demon Sect
ravaged the Central Plains.

68
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,800
Countless martial artists died.

69
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,199
To stop the Demon Sect,

70
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,839
the major sects formed an alliance

71
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,959
and laid siege
to its headquarters at Busi Sea.

72
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:34,800
Do you all remember that battle?

73
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,839
Amitabha.

74
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:40,360
I had the honor
of fighting in that battle

75
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,279
alongside Shaolin Temple's former abbot.

76
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:44,800
I remember it clearly to this day.

77
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:49,680
The Demon Sect leader, Master Baiyi,

78
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:53,319
defeated the leaders
of all eight sects single-handedly.

79
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:56,000
Not one of them survived.

80
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,720
Even now,

81
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:02,759
the thought of his power
sends chills down my spine.

82
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:05,600
I've heard of that battle, too.

83
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,600
They say Master Baiyi

84
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:10,199
was nearly spent by the end of it.

85
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,279
Only Mr. Murong

86
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,600
and an unknown hero named Peng

87
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,959
still had the strength to fight.

88
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,879
They pressed their advantage

89
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,800
and together sent Master Baiyi

90
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,319
plunging into the abyss
of Youming Valley.

91
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,800
From then on,

92
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,920
Master Baiyi was never heard from again.

93
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,519
The Demon Sect scattered

94
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,720
and never rose again.

95
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,199
You're right,

96
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,399
except for one detail.

97
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:39,240
Master Baiyi had wounded me so badly

98
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,199
that I could no longer fight.

99
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:43,519
The hero you mentioned

100
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,800
defeated that fiend alone

101
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,120
and sent him into the abyss.

102
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:49,439
But the battle drained all his strength,

103
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,120
and he had little time left.

104
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:54,560
Why bring up a battle

105
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,680
from over twenty years ago, Mr. Murong?

106
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,879
That's right.

107
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,759
That hero's name

108
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:02,600
was Peng Zhen.

109
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,800
He was my sworn brother.

110
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:10,360
And his connection to Mr. Peng here

111
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,120
runs very deep.

112
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,759
After that battle,

113
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:17,079
Mr. Peng Zhen
knew his days were numbered.

114
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,959
To protect his child
from the Demon Sect's revenge,

115
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:24,360
he decided to send his infant son

116
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:26,680
back to his sect for protection.

117
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,920
When he made that decision,

118
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:33,240
he made me swear
to guard the secret with my life.

119
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,560
That's why I've kept it hidden
all these years.

120
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:37,160
Mr. Murong,

121
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,279
what are you trying to say?

122
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,000
Mr. Peng Zhen belonged to

123
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,160
the Wuhuduandao Sect,

124
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:46,199
the same sect you belong to now.

125
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,720
And you, Peng Dasheng,

126
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,879
may be the only child

127
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:51,600
he left in this world.

128
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,120
What?

129
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:54,879
What?

130
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,519
Mr. Peng Zhen's son?

131
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,959
But Mr. Murong,

132
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,399
if my father were from my sect,

133
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:03,000
why would my Master lie to me?

134
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:04,680
That's simple.

135
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:08,199
He was afraid you'd avenge your father

136
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:10,000
and make an enemy of the Demon Sect.

137
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:13,079
He didn't want you
to meet the same fate as your father.

138
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,319
At the martial tournament,

139
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:17,199
I saw the soul jade around your neck.

140
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,560
I remember it well.

141
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:21,959
Peng Zhen always wore it.

142
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:23,360
You also said

143
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:25,480
your father left it to you.

144
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,519
Besides,

145
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:28,920
your age matches perfectly.

146
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,639
Could all that really

147
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:33,079
be a coincidence?

148
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,319
But Master,

149
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,399
what was my father like?

150
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,360
He...

151
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,040
He was the outer disciple

152
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:46,160
my late master valued most.

153
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:49,399
Twenty years ago,
your father brought you to the sect

154
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,800
and never came back.

155
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,199
But since he left you

156
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:55,199
the soul jade,

157
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,959
he must have had a reason.

158
00:07:57,120 --> 00:08:00,319
When the time is right,
you'll understand.

159
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,199
(Could this be the right time)

160
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:05,399
(Master spoke of?)

161
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,759
Amitabha.

162
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,040
Mr. Murong

163
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,920
was there himself.

164
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,279
He spoke with certainty.

165
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,560
It must be true.

166
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,399
Mr. Peng Zhen gave his life
for a righteous cause.

167
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:21,399
That truly commands respect.

168
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:24,360
I've long heard
of Mr. Peng Zhen's great deeds.

169
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,319
Now that I've seen his son,

170
00:08:26,319 --> 00:08:30,120
I see he's every bit his father's son.

171
00:08:32,399 --> 00:08:33,519
Sect leaders,

172
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,639
fellow martial artists,

173
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,960
look at this Heroes' Monument.

174
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,799
The inscription

175
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:42,399
was written by Mr. Peng Zhen himself.

176
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:45,799
(Heroes' Monument)
It reads, "A hero uses his strength

177
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,279
not to harm, but to protect the people."

178
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,480
Those words became
the martial world's guiding principle.

179
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,759
Mr. Peng Zhen once protected

180
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:54,399
the martial world single-handedly.

181
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,600
Now, his son

182
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,600
stands before us.

183
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:01,159
Wouldn't his son

184
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:02,799
be a fitting choice

185
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,600
to lead the allied forces?

186
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,679
That makes sense.

187
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,279
Amitabha.

188
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:14,600
He gave his life
defending the righteous path.

189
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:18,559
Now, his son has rid the martial world
of a great menace.

190
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:21,519
Shaolin Temple
will give him our full support

191
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:24,799
and nominate him
as commander of the allied forces.

192
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,919
Kongtong Sect has no objections.

193
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,600
With Mr. Peng leading us,

194
00:09:28,759 --> 00:09:30,600
we'll carry on his father's will

195
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,799
and wipe out the Demon Sect's remnants.

196
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:34,799
Kunlun Sect supports him, too.

197
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:36,159
Gaojiang Sect supports him.

198
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:38,879
So do I. I support him.

199
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:40,320
So do I. I support him, too.

200
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,399
Since there are no objections,

201
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:43,600
each sect will send

202
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,679
its best fighters

203
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:46,919
to join the allied forces.

204
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,200
Peng Dasheng will command them.

205
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,480
Tomorrow, we march

206
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,559
on Liuchu Manor

207
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:53,000
to destroy the Demon Sect

208
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,159
and restore peace and order
to the martial world.

209
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,799
Destroy the Demon Sect!

210
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,159
Defend the martial world!

211
00:09:59,159 --> 00:10:00,480
Destroy the Demon Sect!

212
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,679
Defend the martial world!

213
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,039
Destroy the Demon Sect!

214
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:04,399
Defend the martial world!

215
00:10:04,519 --> 00:10:05,799
Destroy the Demon Sect!

216
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:07,159
Defend the martial world!

217
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,519
Destroy the Demon Sect!

218
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:09,879
Defend the martial world!

219
00:10:09,919 --> 00:10:10,559
Destroy the Demon Sect!

220
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:20,879
Master,

221
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,720
we march tomorrow.

222
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,279
Why are you still up?

223
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:28,559
Do you really think
Peng Zhen was my father?

224
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:36,360
Whether he was or not
doesn't really matter.

225
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,679
Then what does?

226
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,399
What matters is that

227
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,879
this new identity gives you

228
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,320
the standing you need

229
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,519
to do what you want.

230
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:49,000
The Luocha Blade Demon

231
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,960
is bound to show up at Liuchu Manor.

232
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:53,720
It'll be your best chance
to avenge Xiaojiu.

233
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,720
You're right.

234
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,519
I should focus

235
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:00,080
on the battle at Liuchu Manor.

236
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:03,159
Avenging Xiaojiu comes first.

237
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,120
No one knows who will make it back
from Liuchu Manor.

238
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:08,200
Those sect leaders

239
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,000
won't risk themselves
unless they have to.

240
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:12,759
Master, you must be careful.

241
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,360
Changsheng, do you believe in fate?

242
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:17,159
My master said
this tribulation was fated

243
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:20,000
and that I was doomed to die.

244
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,759
If your master already warned you,

245
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:23,720
why go against fate?

246
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,919
Because I don't believe in fate.

247
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:28,360
Master always says fate can't be defied.

248
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,120
Yet he still did

249
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,000
everything he could to keep me alive.

250
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,080
If he could defy fate
and change my fate,

251
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:37,679
why can't I break free of it?

252
00:11:37,919 --> 00:11:38,480
But Master,

253
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,440
do you really think
you can tear open the sky?

254
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,279
And what if I do?

255
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:47,399
If Heaven truly decides our lives,

256
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,879
then I'll fight Heaven itself.

257
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:52,080
I'll make heaven and earth
my battlefield

258
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,679
and the stars my blades.

259
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,159
Even if it destroys me,

260
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,679
I won't be afraid.

261
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,559
Wouldn't that be

262
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,399
a life worth living?

263
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,799
I'm old now.

264
00:12:07,879 --> 00:12:09,759
All I can do is help where I can.

265
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:12,399
The Seven-Leaf Revival Herb on
Yunwu Cliff should be ready to harvest.

266
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:14,960
It's gentle enough

267
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:18,200
to keep the spiritual power
inside you under control.

268
00:12:18,399 --> 00:12:19,919
I'll go pick it

269
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:21,799
and clear my head

270
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,320
in the mountains while I'm there.

271
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:27,080
Master, we march tomorrow.

272
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:29,600
You should get some rest.

273
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:48,720
Father.

274
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:54,120
Your wounds haven't healed.

275
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,159
You need to rest.

276
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:56,600
Go back to your room.

277
00:12:57,159 --> 00:12:57,759
Father,

278
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:00,480
you know Liuchu Manor
is a Demon Sect trap.

279
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,279
Why did you nominate Peng Dasheng

280
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:03,600
to command the allied forces?

281
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:05,320
Aren't you sending him to his death?

282
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:10,000
Everything I've done

283
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:12,000
is for you.

284
00:13:12,399 --> 00:13:13,399
For me?

285
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:17,399
I can tell you've fallen for him.

286
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,200
But he comes from humble origins

287
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,559
and isn't a suitable match for you.

288
00:13:20,759 --> 00:13:23,600
Gild a clay idol,
and people will worship it.

289
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,080
But as he is now,

290
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,559
he can barely protect himself.

291
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:30,279
I'm making him the commander

292
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:32,480
to pave the way for him.

293
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:34,320
But at the Martial Arts Assembly,

294
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,200
you said he was Mr. Peng Zhen's son.

295
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:39,600
Was that a lie?

296
00:13:39,679 --> 00:13:41,080
Bingqing, remember this.

297
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:43,320
Who Peng Dasheng really is
doesn't matter.

298
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:45,799
What matters is that
you have feelings for him.

299
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,399
If he still doesn't know
what's good for him,

300
00:13:48,679 --> 00:13:50,320
since I can raise him up,

301
00:13:50,519 --> 00:13:52,000
I can also bring him crashing back down.

302
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,759
But Peng Dasheng saved my life.

303
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,679
I don't care what his background is.

304
00:13:56,159 --> 00:13:57,000
I just want him safe.

305
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:57,519
Don't be foolish.

306
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,759
At the martial tournament,

307
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:02,399
he dared to reject the marriage
in front of everyone.

308
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,960
That alone was reason enough

309
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,759
for me to kill him a hundred times over.

310
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,919
If he weren't one of the finest

311
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:09,279
young martial artists,

312
00:14:09,519 --> 00:14:11,320
and if you hadn't fallen for him,

313
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:15,080
do you think I'd have
let him live this long?

314
00:14:17,399 --> 00:14:19,080
What if the Demon Sect

315
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,720
kills him at Liuchu Manor?

316
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,720
That's my test for him.

317
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:26,080
If he survives,

318
00:14:26,559 --> 00:14:28,759
he'll prove he's worthy of you.

319
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:31,000
If he falls,

320
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,879
then fate wasn't on his side.

321
00:14:33,519 --> 00:14:35,600
And a man cursed by fate

322
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:38,519
is no match for my beloved daughter.

323
00:14:38,799 --> 00:14:39,240
Father...

324
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:39,960
Enough.

325
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,279
Go back to your room and get some rest.

326
00:14:50,879 --> 00:14:51,600
Sir,

327
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:53,200
Peng Dasheng and the others
have left the city.

328
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:57,519
(Bingqing,)

329
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:02,200
(someday, you'll understand
why I did all this.)

330
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:12,100
♪Come on♪

331
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:17,300
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

332
00:15:19,260 --> 00:15:22,220
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

333
00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:25,420
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

334
00:15:25,660 --> 00:15:28,500
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

335
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:31,500
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

336
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:34,980
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

337
00:15:35,220 --> 00:15:38,220
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

338
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:41,300
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

339
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:44,220
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

340
00:15:44,780 --> 00:15:48,100
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

341
00:15:48,140 --> 00:15:51,140
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

342
00:15:51,180 --> 00:15:56,820
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

343
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:59,260
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

344
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:02,340
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

345
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:05,460
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

346
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:09,260
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

347
00:16:09,860 --> 00:16:11,980
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

348
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:15,020
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

349
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:18,460
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

350
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:22,780
♪I am my own king♪

351
00:16:35,860 --> 00:16:37,420
♪I emerge into the world♪

352
00:16:37,420 --> 00:16:39,180
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

353
00:16:39,180 --> 00:16:40,540
♪My pride is my trump card♪

354
00:16:40,540 --> 00:16:42,340
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

355
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:43,740
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

356
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:45,500
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

357
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:47,020
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

358
00:16:47,020 --> 00:16:48,740
♪I dare to break every rule♪

359
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:50,060
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

360
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:51,900
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

361
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:53,140
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

362
00:16:53,140 --> 00:16:55,380
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

363
00:16:55,380 --> 00:16:56,900
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

364
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:58,500
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

365
00:16:58,500 --> 00:17:00,100
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

366
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,820
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

367
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:03,540
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

368
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:04,900
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

369
00:17:04,900 --> 00:17:06,540
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

370
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:08,020
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

371
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,740
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

372
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:11,340
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

373
00:17:11,340 --> 00:17:12,900
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

374
00:17:12,900 --> 00:17:17,220
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

375
00:17:17,220 --> 00:17:19,380
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

376
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:21,980
♪Let me write the legend♪

377
00:17:26,860 --> 00:17:29,420
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

378
00:17:29,420 --> 00:17:32,740
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

379
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:35,220
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

380
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:39,300
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

381
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:42,260
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

382
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:44,740
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

383
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:47,780
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

384
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:52,820
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
